##################################################################
##	This software is to be used in conjunction with ccMiner. Get the original miner :
##	
##	https://github.com/cbuchner1/ccminer/releases
##	
##	Other miners are available. See the forum thread :
##	
##	https://bitcointalk.org/index.php?topic=167229.0
##################################################################

ccManager will automatically run ccMiner.

mailutils will require to be installed and setup if you want to take advantage of email alerts.

http://mailutils.org/
http://www.ubuntututorials.com/send-email-command-line-ubuntu/


Open config/config.conf file and set the important variables...

You must set the path to your ccMiner :

	- declare path_to_ccminer_dir=~/your/path/to/ccminer_folder

You must tell ccManager which GPU's to use : 

	- declare -r pool_gpus=0

You must tell ccManager which pools to use for primary and secondary.
When you have your configurations set, cd into the ccManager directory and execute "./ccManager.sh" without the quotes.
	
DO NOT run ccMiner, this program runs the miner for you.
	
If you want email alerts, you must configure mailutils - see above!

